You Can Host A Fundraiser Challenge Your Friends To Raise Funds To Rescue Survivors Of Human Trafficking.

Start A Fundraiser
{/* banner */}

Start YOUR FUNDRAISER

Have your goal in mind? You’re ready to set up your fundraiser! Follow the steps through the link below to launch, and make sure to upload a personal message and photo that lets your friends and family know why the fight against human trafficking is important to you.

Let People Know

It’s time to share your fundraiser with friends and family on social media, through text, or in real life! Make posts or videos and re-share facts and stories from @Sex & Trafficking

We can help! Our special graphics and captions will help you rally your community for freedom. Make sure to download the social shareables here!

{/* Fund Raiser */}

Start Your Fundraiser

Fill out this simple form to start your fundraiser that frees kids from slavery!
